The '''Imperial Department of Redesign''', also known as the '''Imperial Redesign Team''', was an elite, highly secretive corps of the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]], tasked with subduing or liquidating troublesome non-[[Human/Legends|Human]] species, which was to be achieved through the secret project "[[The Heart of Steel]]." [[Grand Moff/Legends|Grand Moff]] [[4-8C]], an [[IG-series/Legends|IG-series]] [[Assassin droid/Legends|assassin droid]], was one of their number. It was founded by [[Janus Greejatus/Legends|Janus Greejatus]], member of the [[Imperial Ruling Council/Legends|Imperial Ruling Council]], [[Dark side adept/Legends|Dark Side Adept]] and a noted [[Humanocentrism|humanocentrist]] who had been involved with [[Palpatine/Legends|Darth Sidious]] since the latter's time as [[Supreme Chancellor/Legends|Supreme Chancellor]].

